snippet.title: Amber Heard Looking Uncomfortable Arriving For Deposition Against Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Saturday, August 13, 2016 - Amber Heard arrives for her scheduled deposition in her domestic abuse and divorce case against Johnny Depp. Her lawyers walk beside her, as the 30-year-old actress heads to the court looking a bit uncomfortable and wearing the same outfit as she did for her last deposition meeting. Meanwhile she and her lawyers are asked about the recently leaked video tape, in which Depp is captured being very angry.
